title: LUXURY CONDO WATER VIEW IN BISCAYNE BEACH!!
posting_body: ['Biscayne Beach condos is a luxury high-rise development in Edgewater rising 51 stories and with 388 traditional condo residences plus 3 live-work condo units.', 'Biscayne Beach, completed in 2017, was designed by architecture firm WHLC Architecture and developed by Eastview Development and GTIS Partners.', 'The amenities will keep you active with tennis & basketball courts, beach and pool cabana service, a beach/pool club bar, an outdoor fire pit, beach volleyball, jet ski and kayak rentals, library, theater, and pool tables.', 'The lobby of Biscayne Beach includes a fine dining restaurant, beauty salon, and art gallery for guests and residents.', 'Edgewater is one of Miami’s hippest, new neighborhoods that puts residents in the heart of it all.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
